            <div class="pipe-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="pipe-step"><div class="ps-num">02</div><div class="ps-name">Decompose</div></div>
            <div class="pipe-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="pipe-step"><div class="ps-num">03</div><div class="ps-name">Classify</div></div>
            <div class="pipe-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="pipe-step"><div class="ps-num">04</div><div class="ps-name">Map Forms</div></div>
            <div class="pipe-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="pipe-step"><div class="ps-num">05</div><div class="ps-name">Score</div></div>
            <div class="pipe-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="pipe-step"><div class="ps-num">06</div><div class="ps-name">Output Plan</div></div>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Ingest methods:</strong> Local folder · ZIP archive · Git URL · Pasted code</p>
        <p><strong>Output files:</strong> <code style="color:var(--gold);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:0.9rem;">SalvageBotX_PLAN.md</code> (human-readable) and <code style="color:var(--gold);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:0.9rem;">salvagebotx_plan.json</code> (machine-readable for pipeline integration)</p>
    </div>

